# Loading & Mutation Strategy

## 1. GET Requests (Queries)
- Data fetching using `useQuery` MUST handle loading states locally. 
- Use local `<Skeleton />` components. DO NOT use global loaders for GET requests.
- Returning a full-page loader for GET requests is forbidden.

## 2. Global Mutations (Standard POST/PUT/DELETE)
- Standard data mutations using `useMutation` MUST NOT implement manual local loading overlays.
- Rely on the `GlobalMutationLoader` (which uses `useIsMutating`) to block the screen.
- You MUST still disable the submit button locally while `mutation.isPending` is true.

## 3. Notes
- The global mutation loader blocks interaction for any mutation across the app.